Popular Nollywood actress, Mercy Aigbe, got her fans talking as she recently took to her Instagram page to share a beautiful photo she took with her mother. In the photo, the 42-year-old actress was captured smiling beside her beautiful ageless mum. Aigbe wore a leopard print gown and sunglasses while her mum donned an Ankara outfit. Sharing the photo, the actress simply wrote, “Iya Mercy“ READ ALSO [Video] Nigerian man beaten to death in India, FG reacts Fans of the actress have trooped to the comment sections to compliment the actress and her mum and some even pointed out their striking resemblance.